setDestNoiseMap

public void setDestNoiseMap(NoiseMap destNoiseMap)
Sets the destination noise map.

Parameters:
destNoiseMap - The destination noise map. The destination noise map will contain the coherent-noise values from this noise map after a successful call to the build() method. The destination noise map must exist throughout the lifetime of this object unless another noise map replaces that noise map.

setSourceModule

public void setSourceModule(ModuleBase sourceModule)
Sets the source module.

Parameters:
sourceModule - The source module. This object fills in a noise map with the coherent-noise values from this source module. The source module must exist throughout the lifetime of this object unless another noise module replaces that noise module.
